<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ida82ae499-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s897"><num value="897">§ 897.</num><heading> Art. 97. Unlawful detention</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any person subject to this chapter who, except as provided by law, apprehends, arrests, or confines any person shall be punished as a court-martial may direct.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ida82ae49a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041">Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70A/69">70A Stat. 69</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
